detaileddescription.para: The resource consumption cannot be explicitly defined for BAPHandler_PSO_ImExport and BAPHandler_UtilityLib libraries. Potential influence on specific resource consumption should be considered from the perspective of specific SWC which is using functions from these libraries. The library BAPHandler_PSO_ImExport serve the Active Participant functionality and handle PSO_ImExport functionality, what influence in recognized manner on resource consumption, but should be considered as a part of resource consuption of specific SWC which is using this library (as was reflected in SWA in relevant architecture decision).

The library BAPHandler_UtilityLib collects simple helper funtions which has minimal impact on performance, memory consumption or CPU Load and also should be considered as a part of resource consuption of specific SWC which is using this library.
Performance: The performance objectives were not defined for these libraries and are not mentioned in the SWA.
Memory Consumption: The memory consumption objectives were not defined for these libraries and are not mentioned in the SWA.
CPU Load: The CPU load objectives were not defined for these libraries and are not mentioned in the SWA.
